title.narrative: China Bengbu Integrated Environment Improvement Project

description.narrative: The project development objective is to improve the effectiveness and sustainability of selected urban environmental services delivered in Bengbu Municipality through improving water supply, reducing incidents of land submergence from flooding, and enhancing wastewater management.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA Annex A, Subsidiary Agreements, para 9 (a) | Description :BDC & B3WTC to prod. for each FY beginning in FY2010, total rev. more than the sum of its total operating exp. and the amt by which debt service requirements exceed the prov. fordepreciations. | Due Date :31-Dec-2010

Finance Agreement :PA Annex A, Subsidiary Agreements, para 9 (b) & (c) | Description :On the basis of forecasts, Project Companiesreview whether they would meet the requirements of para 9(a) above, and take the necessary actions to ensure such requirements aremet. | Due Date :15-Aug-2010

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 1 (a) | Description :PIE shall cause Bengbu to carry out a study on institutional reformsnecessary to optimize the efficiency of water-related sector agencies and furnish the results to the Bank. | Due Date :15-Feb-2011

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 1 (b) | Description :PIE shall cause Bengbu to begin implementation of recommendations of saidstudy, taking into account the Bank's comments thereon. | Due Date :15-Aug-2011

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 2 (a) | Description :PIE shall cause WCIC to enter into a contract with a professionalmanagement company, to manage infrastructure services in MIZ in Wuhe County. | Due Date :15-Aug-2012
Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 2 (b) | Description :PIE shall cause WCIC to introduce load-based charges for industrialwastewater treatment within MIZ. | Due Date :15-Aug-2012

Finance Agreement :PA, Section IV. 3 (a) | Description :PIE shall cause Bengbu to furnish to the Bank a time-bound action plan forreducing pollution by chemical industries in Bengbu. | Due Date :15-Feb-2009
